Source: sigar
Section: java
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Apollon Oikonomopoulos <apoikos@gmail.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9), perl, python2.7-dev, ant, liblog4j1.2-java,
               junit, ant-contrib-cpptasks, python-all-dev, openjdk-6-jdk
